relation: Beg, Borrow Or Steal Aka"Puppets On A Staaldraad"
Nice Boys Don't Play Rock And Roll
FA: J. Fisher, retro Bolted A. Davies. Dec. 2003

35m ! The route starts to the right of "Master Of Puppets" and crosses over at the fourth bolt and then carries on to the top of the crag. Lower to chains of "Me Or My Girl". A 70 meter rope is advisable. You can get down on a 60 if the belayer moves up to the ledge on the right.
The route starts to the right of "Sanatorium", bouldery start, named after Rudolfs boys.
The route furthest to the right.

Routes from the far LEFT of the crag towards the right (i.e. back towards the car park) Legoland is Montagu's most popular climbing area due to the easier grade of routes and quick access. Legoland is child friendly and dogs are allowed.
